Operation invoiceAddAvailableCreditPayment

public invoiceAddAvailableCreditPayment(string $debit_number, OrderAvailableCreditPaymentRequest $payment) : PaymentResponse

Add a payment to a given debit using the customer's available credit. If a specific amount is specified to use but there is less than that available, an error will be thrown. If a zero amount is specified, all or any available credit will be used up to the amount due.

Parameters
$debit_number : string

The debit number (usually an order number) to apply the credit to. (required)

$payment : OrderAvailableCreditPaymentRequest

An AvailableCreditPaymentRequest object. (required)
